thread.title: Corinne Leake
thread.title_full: Elevate Styles reviewed by Corinne Leake

author: Corinne Leake
title: Corinne Leake
text: Super fast delivery using standard shipping. I ordered on tues and received it on friday. Now me and Lolita (my wig) are doing great! Great wig, soft, shiny but not plasticky,l. The lace was a little rough, but im sure that will be amended once i cut it. Otherwise awesome product and great company.
